Titolo: Arms (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Arms is a 3D fighting game developed and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo Switch home video game console, which released on June 16, 2017. The game differentiates itself from standard fighting games with its unconventional fighting system where every playable character fights with long range attacks and up to four players can choose a fighter and battle using a variety of extendable, weaponized arms to knock out opponents in a three-dimensional arena. 
Arms received generally favourable reviews from critics and sold over two million copies as of July 2018, making it one of the best-selling games on the Switch.



Genere: Fighting 

Valutazione: N/A
